Kc2 Kf7 {[pgndiagram] Is trivial win}) 43... Be5 44. Rxh7 Kf7 45. Rh1 g5 46.
Re1 Kf6 47. Rg1 Kg6 48. Re1 Bf6 49. Rg1 g4 50. fxg4 f4 51. g5 Bd4 52. Rd1 Be3
53. Kxc3 Bc1 54. Rd6+ Kxg5 55. Rb6 f3 56. Kd3 Kf4 57. Rb8 Kg3 {[pgndiagram]
Very convincing and important victory for Keres.} 0-1

